job_description:
Intro
Onze verontschuldigingen, dit bericht is alleen beschikbaar in Amerikaans Engels.
Responsibilities
Learn and grow with the help of more experienced colleagues;
Design, build and test well-written Spring Boot microservices;
Collaborate and discuss problems and solutions in a cross-functional team, support Frontend Team, QA Team and Product Owners / Scrum Master to meet the requirements goals;
Deploy software and services to Kubernetes clusters and other application containers.
Requirements
+1,5 years professional experience developing in Java;
Development with Java 8+;
Experience with version control systems such as Git.
Experience with Spring;
Nice to have:
Experience with Maven;
Experience with Spring Boot;
Experience working with relational and NoSql databases;
Experience with containers (ex: Docker), microservices (REST or SOAP) and cloud infrastructure services.
Personal traits:
Team Leading skills;
Desire to innovate and investigate new technologies;
Ability to work well in a team, self-driven and eager to learn;
Creative thinking, analytical skills, with attention to detail;
Fluent in English.
Details
Location Europe
 Urgency Hot vacancy
 Contract Freelance
 Open for English speaking Yes
 Visa support No
 Period 1+years
 Remote Yes
